      "checked icon is check_box, color system/fg/primary (#615fff) idle/hover/focused; system/fg/active (#4f39f6) pressed",
      "indeterminate icon is indeterminate_check_box, same colors as checked",
      "disabled: all selection types use system/fg/disabled (#cad5e2)",
      "focused: 2px border in system/border/interactive/focused (#615fff80); radius 2px (s) / 4px (m)",
      "no inverse axis — no dark-background variants",
      "variant format: size={s|m}, state={idle|hover|pressed|focused|disabled}, selection type={unchecked|checked|indeterminate}"
